title: Brida 2024 data files
metadata.description:
This dataset contains the following related to Brida et al 2024 Science Advances

  • All Prism files supporting conclusions of this publication
  • Histological validation of targeting for behavioral experiments
  • The processed Seurat object for CRISPRi Reln knockdown snRNAseq experiment presented in Figure 4 ("allRats_souped_noDoub.rds")
  • csv's for supplemental figures S5 & S8
metadata.journal.title: Science Advances
